com.ziluck.factions.base

  • Packages that use com.ziluck.factions.base 
    Package Description
    com.ziluck.factions
    Classes that touch all aspects of the plugin.
    com.ziluck.factions.api.commands
    The API that drives the command system.
    com.ziluck.factions.base
    Location for the base entities that make up Factions.
    com.ziluck.factions.base.claims
    The base for claim wrappers.
    com.ziluck.factions.commands
    All the commands for the plugin.
    com.ziluck.factions.commands.parsers
    All the parsers for the commands.
    com.ziluck.factions.commands.validators
    All the validators for the commands.
    com.ziluck.factions.configuration
    The classes used to manage the configuration of the project.
    com.ziluck.factions.data
    The in-memory implementations of the base classes.
    com.ziluck.factions.data.mongodb
    Saving Factions entities to MongoDB
    com.ziluck.factions.data.nitrite
    Saving Faction entities to a flat JSON file using Nitrite
    com.ziluck.factions.events
    Events fired by the Factions plugin.
